trans-unit.source: Defines the base class for resources that can be added to an <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 定义可添加到的资源的基类<xref href="System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument"> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: Commits all changes and flushes the resource to the document package.
trans-unit.target: 提交所有更改并刷新到文档包中的资源。

trans-unit.source: Based on settings of <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.XpsSerializationManager> and <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.XpsPackagingPolicy>, such as <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.FontSubsetterCommitPolicies> and <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.PackageInterleavingOrder>, the flush operation of the Commit method may be delayed until the whole <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument> is closed.
trans-unit.target: 根据设置<xref:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.XpsSerializationManager>和<xref:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.XpsPackagingPolicy>，如<xref:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.FontSubsetterCommitPolicies>和<xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.PackageInterleavingOrder>，Commit 方法的刷新操作可能推迟到整个<xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument>已关闭。</xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument> </xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.PackageInterleavingOrder> </xref:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.FontSubsetterCommitPolicies> </xref:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.XpsPackagingPolicy> </xref:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.XpsSerializationManager>

trans-unit.target: 当在派生类中重写，则返回读取或写入资源的 I/O 的流。
